## ✅ **COMPLETED FEATURES**

### **Phase 1: Core Platform (v1.0.0 - v2.0.0)**
- [x] **42+ Trading Strategies** - Breakout, Trend, Mean Reversion, Momentum, Hybrid, Advanced
- [x] **Strategy Registry** - Auto-registration system
- [x] **Backtest Engine** - GPU/CPU accelerated execution
- [x] **Data Manager** - CCXT integration + SQLite caching
- [x] **Risk Manager** - Position sizing and risk management
- [x] **Technical Indicators** - TA-Lib wrapper with 50+ indicators

### **Phase 2: MCP Integration (v2.0.0)**
- [x] **MCP Server** - Model Context Protocol implementation
- [x] **16 MCP Tools** - Complete Claude Desktop integration
- [x] **Batch Processing** - 20-30x faster multi-strategy comparison
- [x] **Response Optimization** - 3KB vs 500KB (166x smaller)
- [x] **Full Year Data Fetch** - 364 days, 8760 candles verified
- [x] **System Prompts** - Optimized Claude Desktop interaction

### **Phase 3: FastAPI Backend (v3.0.0)** ⭐ **CURRENT**
- [x] **FastAPI Application** - Production-grade REST API
- [x] **11 REST Endpoints** - Strategies, Backtest, Optimization, Market, Portfolio
- [x] **Pydantic Models** - Type-safe request/response validation
- [x] **OpenAPI Documentation** - Interactive Swagger UI
- [x] **CORS Middleware** - Frontend-ready
- [x] **Error Handling** - Comprehensive exception management
- [x] **Code Reuse** - Zero duplication with MCP server

### **Optimization & Validation**
- [x] **Genetic Algorithm** - Parameter optimization
- [x] **Walk-Forward Analysis** - Time-series validation
- [x] **K-Fold Validation** - Cross-validation
- [x] **Monte Carlo Simulation** - Risk analysis
- [x] **Portfolio Optimization** - Equal Weight, Risk Parity, Max Sharpe, Min Variance
- [x] **Market Regime Detection** - Trending, Ranging, Volatile, Quiet

---

## 🚀 **CURRENT SPRINT: Sprint 1 - Real-Time Trading Foundation**

**Duration:** Week 1 (Nov 21-28, 2025)  
**Goal:** Enable real-time signal generation and tracking

### **1. Signal Scanner** ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ **HIGHEST PRIORITY**

**Objective:** Scan multiple symbols for active trading signals in real-time.

**Why:** Enables actual trading immediately!

**Features:**
- [ ] Multi-symbol scanning (10-50 symbols)
- [ ] Strategy-agnostic (works with all 42+ strategies)
- [ ] Real-time signals (latest 500 candles)
- [ ] Signal strength (confidence 0-1)
- [ ] Entry/SL/TP calculations
- [ ] JSON export
- [ ] REST API endpoint (`POST /api/v1/scanner/scan`)

**Estimate:** 6-8 hours  
**Status:** 🎯 Ready to start!

---

### **2. Experiment Manager** ⭐⭐⭐⭐

**Objective:** Track and organize all backtesting experiments.

**Why:** Essential for systematic research and comparison.

**Features:**
- [ ] Experiment configuration (YAML/JSON)
- [ ] Database schema (SQLite)
- [ ] Run management
- [ ] Comparison tools
- [ ] Export results (CSV/JSON)
- [ ] REST API endpoints

**Estimate:** 8-10 hours  
**Status:** Ready after Signal Scanner

---

### **3. Strategy Templates + CLI** ⭐⭐⭐

**Objective:** Streamline strategy development.

**Why:** Reduce friction for creating new strategies.

**Features:**
- [ ] CLI command (`smarttrade new-strategy`)
- [ ] 4 base templates
- [ ] Auto-registration
- [ ] Parameter hints
- [ ] Test generation

**Estimate:** 4-6 hours  
**Status:** Nice to have (if time permits)

---

